    "Enhancing drafting One advantage of writing with GPT was that I could break some parts of writing down either by tasks or sections so that I could efficiently develop an initial draft.",
    "For example, while I write, GPT is searching for relevant evidence.",
    "Or I write an introduction and body and GPT works on the conclusion since it's more about a summary of an essay. 4.",
    "Enhancing revision It was great to work with and consult with an AI system to further develop and clarify ideas, and restructure the text after an initial draft.",
